import React from 'react'
import {  BrowserRouter as Router,  Route, Link} from "react-router-dom";
import {Container, ButtonToolbar,Button, } from '../../node_modules/react-bootstrap-icons'
import anasayfa from '../pages/anasayfa'
import hakkimizda from '../pages/hakkimizda'
import iletisim from '../pages/iletisim'


export default function header() {
    return (
        <>
                <Router>
        <Container>
            <ButtonToolbar>
                <Button><Link to="/">Anasayfa</Link></Button> 
                <Button><Link to="/hakkimizda">Blog</Link></Button>
                <Button><Link to="/iletisim">Hakkımızda</Link></Button>
            </ButtonToolbar>
            <ButtonToolbar>
            <Button><Link to="/login">Giriş Yap</Link></Button>
            </ButtonToolbar>
        </Container>


   
         <main >
           <Route path="/anasayfa" component={anasayfa} />
           <Route path="/hakkimizda" component={hakkimizda} />
           <Route path="/iletisim" component={iletisim} />
        </main>

    </Router>
        </>
    )
}
